Sentencas: A nanocomposite Zr/Sm-codoped ceria electrolyte coated with K2CO3/Na2CO3 was synthesized by a coprecipitation method.
Titulo: Ce0.8(SmZr)0.2O2-carbonate nanocomposite electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The electrochemical study of the two-phase nanocomposite electrolytes with carbonate coated on the doped ceria shows high oxygen ion mobility at low temperatures (300-600 degrees C).
Titulo: Ce0.8(SmZr)0.2O2-carbonate nanocomposite electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The interface between the two constituent phases was studied by electrochemical impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Ce0.8(SmZr)0.2O2-carbonate nanocomposite electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: Ionic conductivities were also measured with electrochemical impedance spectroscopy.
Titulo: Ce0.8(SmZr)0.2O2-carbonate nanocomposite electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The morphology and structure of composite electrolyte were characterized using field-emission scanning electron microscopy and X-ray diffraction.
Titulo: Ce0.8(SmZr)0.2O2-carbonate nanocomposite electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: The fuel cell power density is 700 mW cm(-2), and an open-circuit voltage of 1.00 V is achieved at low temperatures (400-550 degrees C).
Titulo: Ce0.8(SmZr)0.2O2-carbonate nanocomposite electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: This codoped approach with a second phase provides a good indication regarding overcoming the challenges of solid oxide fuel cell technology.
Titulo: Ce0.8(SmZr)0.2O2-carbonate nanocomposite electrolyte for solid oxide fuel cell
